column2: "It's just like Xiao said, you really came."
"Oh, it's you. I see... so you're the one Xiao chose. I wonder if you'd call this a coincidence."
"Let's cut the chatter. I'd rather not say something my future self knows."
"Plus, if we don't hurry, we won't make it in time."
"What are we going to do? That's a silly question."
"You came here to change history, right? We're going to kick logic out and do the impossible!"
